HashSet Java ka ek collection class hai jo unique elements
 store karta hai (duplicate allow nahi karta).

👉 Ye Set interface ko implement karta hai aur
internally HashMap ka use karta hai.

Socho tum ek list bana rahe ho:

Apple, Banana, Apple, Mango

👉 HashSet me store karoge to output hoga:

